{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 1 shows the architecture of IoT.",
    "In the following, each of the layers is briefly described.",
    "Application layerThe application layer is where data from IoT devices undergoes processing, analysis, and triggering of actions.",
    "It encompasses applications, services, and software that leverage data gathered from IoT devices to offer insights, make informed choices, and execute operations.",
    "This layer can be tailored to suit diverse applications, ranging from smart homes and industrial automation to healthcare."
  ]
}